{"id": "ccz_app", "n_sys": 3, "n_anc": 0}
```
```python id=app_golden
import numpy as np
golden = np.diag([1,1,1,1,1,1,1,-1]).astype(complex)   # CCZ = controlled-controlled-Z
```
